'''Microsoft To-Do''' is a cloud-based [[task management]] application. It allows users to manage their tasks from a smartphone, tablet and computer. The technology is produced by the team behind [[Wunderlist]], which was acquired by [[Microsoft]], and the stand-alone apps feed into the existing Tasks feature of the [[Microsoft Outlook|Outlook]] product range.

